NSMedieval.BaseTimerController`1[T_REF]:Update+148: 48 8B 75 C8                    - mov rsi,[rbp-38]
NSMedieval.BaseTimerController`1[T_REF]:Update+14c: 48 8B C6                       - mov rax,rsi
