NSMedieval.BaseTimerController`1[T_REF]:Update+159: 85 C0                          - test eax,eax
NSMedieval.BaseTimerController`1[T_REF]:Update+15b: 0F 85 4A 00 00 00              - jne NSMedieval.BaseTimerController`1[T_REF]:Update+1ab
